// Test: ./dk0 --trust-local-package CommonsLang_OCaml get-object CommonsLang_OCaml.MSYS2@2026.6.11 -s Release.Windows_x86_64 -d target/msys2
// MSYS2 tree for `opam init --cygwin-local-install --cygwin-location=<obj>`
// (opam detects MSYS2 via usr/bin/cygpath.exe). Content = the pinned
// msys2-base snapshot (msys64/ stripped) plus the msys packages diffutils,
// dos2unix, patch, rsync (with popt+libxxhash), unzip; wget/tar/xz are
// already in base. usr/bin/link.exe is renamed link-coreutils.exe (MSVC
// conflict) and pacman payload metadata is removed, replicating
// gitlab.com/dkml/distributions/msys2-dkml-base. make is omitted:
// consumers use CommonsBase_GNU.Make.
